subproject.corporate outcome: Enhanced national capacity to use ICT for development as driver for pro-poor capacity development and institutional building
subproject.description:
1. Inter agency collaboration and exchange of data are enhanced by integrating national databases through ICT.
2. Increased efficiency, transparency and accountability of Public Sector’s Human Resources processes.
3. Government to citizen (G2C) services are enhanced and new channels for service provision established.
4.   E-Government services are promoted and MSAD South South cooperation strategy enhanced
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Support to E-Gov Initiatives
